        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"439483\">Andrew Yang</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/287929-mathlib4/topic/Representing.20Roots.20of.20Irreducible.20Polynomials.20in.20Extension.20F/near/455883473\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=AdjoinRoot#doc\">docs#AdjoinRoot</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Thank you! After some experimentation, I've written the following code. Is this correct?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Polynomial</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">variable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Field</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">variable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">noncomputable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">poly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">^</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- from F to F₀</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F₀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">AdjoinRoot</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">poly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">check</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">AdjoinRoot</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mk</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">poly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- send poly in F to poly in F₀</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">noncomputable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">poly_in_F₀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">poly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">map</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">S</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">AdjoinRoot</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">poly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">)))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">AdjoinRoot</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">of</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">poly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- send a to a in F₀</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">noncomputable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">new_x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">AdjoinRoot</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">of</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">poly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- the root of poly in F₀</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">noncomputable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">AdjoinRoot</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">root</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">poly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">checkroot</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">eval</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">AdjoinRoot</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">poly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">)))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">z</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">poly_in_F₀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">unfold</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">poly_in_F₀</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">unfold</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">z</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IsRoot</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">eq_zero</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">AdjoinRoot</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">isRoot_root</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">poly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
